 Welcome back. If you're a familiar face, if you've been in the room, we're so glad you're here.

20
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:17,000
 If you're new to The Porch, thanks for choosing to give up your Tuesday and join us here.

21
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:27,000
 It's amazing just to every single week be a part of worship and see how God is working in the lives of young adults right here in Dallas, Texas.

22
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:34,000
 Like, I know he's doing it in my life, I believe he's doing it in your life, but he's not just doing it here, he's also doing it all over the nation.

23
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:40,000
 He's doing it in rooms just like this, and he's doing it in some of our Porch Live locations.

24
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:44,000
 And we're so grateful that we get to be a part of what God is doing there.

25
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:48,000
 If you're a part of The Porch family, thanks for tuning in with us as well.

26
